《'''红娘公司'''》（{{lang-en|''Love, Inc.''}}）是安德鲁·塞昆达主创的美国电视[[情景喜剧|情景喜剧]]，2005年9月22日至2006年5月11日在[[联合派拉蒙电视网|联合派拉蒙电视网]]首播共一季。[[群戲|主要演员]]包括[[贝茜·菲利普斯|贝茜·菲利普斯]]、[[文斯·维鲁夫|文斯·维鲁夫]]、[[里根·戈麦斯-普雷斯顿|里根·戈麦斯-普雷斯顿]]、[[艾恩·奥福曼|艾恩·奥福曼]]和[[霍利·罗宾森·皮特|霍利·罗宾森·皮特]]，围绕[[約會|婚介所]]工作的五名[[媒人|媒人]]展开。节目由蔡斯电视、利特菲尔德公司、伯格－科尔斯电视和派拉蒙电视网制作，除联合派拉蒙电视网首播外，还通过[[天空见证台|LivingTV]]和[[芬兰第四台|芬兰第四台]]分别在英国和芬兰播映。亚当·蔡斯、沃伦·利特菲尔德、马克·伯格与[[奥伦·科尔斯|奥伦·科尔斯]]担任执行制作人。

节目原定名《约会女搭档》，本是专为推动[[莎侬·多赫提|莎侬·多赫提]]事业设计的情愿喜剧处女作。联合派拉蒙电视网订购后认为预播观众对多赫提反响不佳，决定由菲利普斯取代。剧中情节发生在纽约，实际取景地是洛杉矶好莱坞[[派拉蒙影業|派拉蒙制片厂]]及加利福尼亚州其他地点。节目富含当代嘻哈音乐，联合派拉蒙电视网大力宣传，旨在吸引城镇居民观看，与《[[阿傑出少年|阿傑出少年]]》一起在周四晚播映。

《红娘公司》在拉美裔少女人群的收视率很高，但整体收视成绩很不理想，2006年联合派拉蒙电视网与[[WB電視網|WB電視網]]合并组建[[CW電視網|CW電視網]]后取消。本剧与其他[[黑人情景喜剧|黑人情景喜剧]]停播引发评论界反弹，媒体批评此举导致电视上的非裔美国演员和角色减少。评论员对节目看法不一，部分文章称赞剧中人物种族多样化，但批评剧情和人物缺乏新意，菲利普斯的演出无法让观众信服。节目停播后没有发行蓝光影碟或DVD。

== 剧情架构 ==
红娘公司是纽约的婚介所，雇员都是一心想找到另一半的单身狗。刚离婚的克丽娅·拉沃（{{lang|en|Clea Lavoy}}）是公司创始人和业主，请朋友兼雇员丹妮丝·约翰逊（{{lang|en|Denise Johnson}}）帮忙再找伴侣。丹妮丝非常热心，但老板的寻爱之路依然困难重重。克丽娅此前的婚姻看起来很幸福，而且持续近十年，是红娘公司最重要的活广告，所以她离婚为公司前景蒙上阴影。公司其他雇员包括前台维维亚娜（{{lang|en|Viviana}}）、形象专家弗朗辛（{{lang|en|Francine}}）、技术员兼摄影师巴里（{{lang|en|Barry}}）。<ref name="Premise1">{{cite web | url = https://www.popmatters.com/love-inc-050922-2496226165.html | title = Love Stinks | last = Ramlow | first = Todd R. | date = 2005-09-22 | publisher = PopMatters Media, Inc. | work = [[PopMatters|PopMatters]] | dead-url = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201201091104/https://www.popmatters.com/love-inc-050922-2496226165.html | access-date = 2021-02-07 | archive-date = 2020-12-01 }}</ref><ref name="Premise2">{{cite book | last = Muir | first = John Kenneth | title = TV Year: The Prime Time 2005–2006 Season | year = 2007 | publisher = Applause Theatre | location = New York | isbn = 978-1-55783-684-7 | access-date = 2021-02-07 | page = 86 | url = https://archive.org/details/tvyearvolume1pri0000muir}}</ref>

节目分集大多介绍公司内部运作，如第一个女同性恋客户、与昔日神父约会，以及旨在吸引宅男和[[廣場恐懼症|廣場恐懼症]]患者的营销策略<ref name="Premise2" />。公司雇员充当客户的约会搭档和“守护天使”，帮他们克服交流障碍<ref name="Advisory">{{cite news | archive-date = 2016-07-11 | access-date = 2021-02-07 | dead-url = no | url = https://www.latimes.com/archives/la-xpm-2005-sep-22-wk-love22-story.html | title = Don't make a date with 'Love, Inc.' | last = Brownfieldl | date = 2005-09-22 | publisher = Tronc, Inc. | newspaper = Los Angeles Times | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160711082741/http://articles.latimes.com/2005/sep/22/news/wk-love22 | first = Pau }}</ref>。各人工作之余都有各种喜剧或爱情历险经历，例如维维亚娜一心想嫁给美国公民获取[[美国永久居民|绿卡]]<ref name="Premise1" />；丹妮丝虽然工作实力出众，能让客户与“看起来无法企及的灵魂伴侣”配对，但她本人却一直没找到真爱<ref name="Premise3">{{cite web | archive-date = 2006-09-09 | access-date = 2006-09-09 | url = http://www.upn.com/shows/love_inc/about.shtml | title = About the Show | publisher = UPN | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20060909085421/http://www.upn.com/shows/love_inc/about.shtml | dead-url = yes }}</ref>。

== 人物 ==
《红娘公司》共有五个主要人物：
* 贝茜·菲利普斯（{{lang|en|Busy Philipps}}）饰丹妮丝·约翰逊，是婚介所约会顾问，自称配对专家，向客户提供“用语指南、服饰指引，以及良好的开场白与结束语”<ref name="Sun2">{{cite news | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200811132329/https://www.sun-sentinel.com/news/fl-xpm-2005-09-22-0509200207-story.html | url = https://www.sun-sentinel.com/news/fl-xpm-2005-09-22-0509200207-story.html | title = Not Much To Love In Upn Series | last = Jicha | first = Tom | date = 2005-09-22 | publisher = Tribune Publishing | newspaper = Sun-Sentinel | archive-date = 2020-08-11 | dead-url = no | access-date = 2021-02-07 }}</ref>。她有“撮合大师”之称<ref name="OldMaid">{{cite journal | url = https://variety.com/2005/tv/reviews/love-inc-2-1200521771/ | title = Review: 'Love, Inc.' | last = Fries | first = Laura | date = 2005-09-18 | journal = [[綜藝_(雜誌)|Variety]] | publisher = Penske Media Corporation | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160818062320/http://variety.com/2005/tv/reviews/love-inc-2-1200521771/ | archive-date = 2016-08-18 | access-date = 2021-02-07 | dead-url = no }}</ref>，但一直没找到真爱。前男友联系贝茜帮他寻找最佳伴侣，此后她对待约会和爱情的态度变得讥诮，自称“充当约会女搭档忙得团团转”。<ref name="Premise1" />菲利普斯认为贝茜的爱情生活“完全是灾难”<ref name="ChicagoBusy">{{cite news | last = Freed | first = David A. | date = 2005-09-12 | access-date = 2021-02-07 | url = https://www.chicagotribune.com/news/ct-xpm-2005-09-12-0509130002-story.html | title = New kids in the box | newspaper = [[芝加哥論壇報|Chicago Tribune]] | publisher = Tronc, Inc. | dead-url = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160817045005/http://articles.chicagotribune.com/2005-09-12/news/0509130002_1_josh-radnor-new-cbs-sitcom-new-kids/2 | archive-date = 2016-08-17 }}</ref>。
* 文斯·维鲁夫（{{lang|en|Vince Vieluf}}）饰婚介所技术员兼摄影师巴里<ref name="OldMaid" /><ref name="Murphy">{{cite web | url = https://www.commonsensemedia.org/tv-reviews/love-inc# | title = Love Inc. | last = Murphy | first = Jill | publisher = Common Sense Media | archive-date = 2017-08-03 | dead-url = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20170803052319/https://www.commonsensemedia.org/tv-reviews/love-inc | accessdate = 2021-02-07 }}</ref>，也是丹妮斯的室友<ref name="Hitch">{{cite web | title = The Futon's First Look: "Love, Inc." (UPN) | url = http://www.thefutoncritic.com/reviews/2005/08/03/the-futons-first-look-love-inc-upn-18923/20050803_loveinc | last = Sullivan | first = Brian Ford | date = 2005-08-03 | publisher = The Futon Critic | access-date = 2021-02-07 | archive-url = https://archive.is/20161121165823/http://www.thefutoncritic.com/reviews/2005/08/03/the-futons-first-look-love-inc-upn-18923/20050803_loveinc// | archive-date = 2016-11-21 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。巴里“[[學者症候群|书呆气十足]]”<ref name="Unbearable">{{Cite news | newspaper = [[今日美國|USA Today]] | archive-date = 2020-04-12 | dead-url = no | url = http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/life/television/reviews/2005-09-21-love-inc_x.htm | title = Funny, there's nothing to 'Love' | first = Robert | date = 2005-10-14 | publisher = [[甘尼特|Gannett Company]] | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200412163153/https://usatoday30.usatoday.com/life/television/reviews/2005-09-21-love-inc_x.htm | last = Bianco | access-date = 2021-02-07 }}</ref>，认为从牙齿到牙膏公司所有关联事物都涉及巨大阴谋<ref name="Doherty5">{{cite news | title = Matchmaker, Matchmaker | last = Heffernan | first = Virginia | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180701194220/https://www.nytimes.com/2005/09/22/arts/television/matchmaker-matchmaker.html | url = https://www.nytimes.com/2005/09/22/arts/television/matchmaker-matchmaker.html | date = 2005-09-22 | newspaper = [[纽约时报|The New York Times]] | publisher = The New York Times Company | archive-date = 2018-07-01 | access-date = 2021-02-07 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。他经常用挠头来交流，但别人根本看不懂<ref name="OldMaid" />，只能理解成他“完全活在不同的层面……乃至不同的星球”<ref name="Cameras">{{cite web | url = http://www.thefutoncritic.com/showatch/love-inc/ | title = About This Show | publisher = [[The_Futon_Critic|The Futon Critic]] | archive-url = https://archive.is/20161121162222/http://www.thefutoncritic.com/showatch/love-inc/ | archive-date = 2016-11-21 | dead-url = no | access-date = 2021-02-07 }}</ref>。据维鲁夫透露，巴里初步设定是“剧中唯一的男子”，也是“世上最幸运的家伙”<ref name="starry magazine">{{cite news | url = http://starrymag.com/vice-vieluf-love-is-all-we-need/ | title = Vice Vieluf – Love Is All We Need | date = 2014-01-13 | work = Starry Constellation Magazine | access-date = 2021-02-07 | dead-url = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20170803053146/http://starrymag.com/vice-vieluf-love-is-all-we-need/ | archive-date = 2017-08-03 }}</ref>。
* 里根·戈麦斯-普雷斯顿（{{lang|en|Reagan Gomez-Preston}}）饰婚介所形象专家弗朗辛，鼓励客户信任她的时尚眼光，为找到伴侣增加胜算<ref name="Cameras" />。她第一次出场就批评克丽娅的打扮像女子篮球队教练，工作时表现活跃、时尚<ref name="Doherty5" />。节目停播时，弗朗辛的剧情尚未充分发展，“仍有些许神秘感”<ref name="Premise1" />。维鲁夫声称弗朗辛的“交流方式完全不同”，生活方式也是如此，与巴里关系特殊<ref name="starry magazine" />。
