== 制作 ==
《红娘公司》原定剧名《约会女搭档》（{{lang|en|''Wing Woman''}}），计划拍成类似《[[情場絕橋王|全民情敌]]》的喜剧<ref name="WingWoman">{{cite web | archive-date = 2016-11-21 | dead-url = no | access-date = 2021-02-07 | url = http://www.thefutoncritic.com/news/2005/02/24/development-update-february-24-17896/6836/ | title = Development Update: February 24 | date = 2005-02-24 | publisher = The Futon Critic | archive-url = https://archive.is/20161121162316/http://www.thefutoncritic.com/news/2005/02/24/development-update-february-24-17896/6836 }}</ref>。节目构想源自《[[纽约时报|纽约时报]]》探导红娘机构的文章<ref name="2019Additions1">{{cite book | last = Gervich | first = Chad | title = Mediabistro.com Presents Small Screen, Big Picture: A Writer's Guide to the TV Business | year = 2008 | publisher = Three Rivers Press | location = New York | access-date = 2021-02-07 | isbn = 978-0-307-39531-3 | url = https://archive.org/details/smallscreenbigpi00gerv}}</ref>，蔡斯电视、利特菲尔德公司、伯格－科尔斯电视和[[派拉蒙电视网|派拉蒙电视网]]共同制作<ref name="Cameras" />。利特菲尔德公司建议电视剧主创安德鲁·塞昆达（{{lang|en|Andrew Secunda}}）和曾参与《[[老友记|老友记]]》的执行制作人亚当·蔡斯（{{lang|en|Adam Chase}}）合作<ref name="WingWoman" /><ref name="2019Additions1" />{{rp|121}}。《红娘公司》的执行制作人还有[[玛尔塔·考夫曼|玛尔塔·考夫曼]]（{{lang|en|Marta Kauffman}}）、丽兹·塔琪萝（{{lang|en|Liz Tuccillo}}）、马克·伯格（{{lang|en|Mark Burg}}）和奥伦·科尔斯（{{lang|en|Oren Koules}}）<ref name="WingWoman" /><ref name="Fodder2">{{cite web | url = http://www.tvfodder.com/archives/2005/09/fall_tv_5_sitco.shtml | title = Fall TV: 4 Sitcoms for Fall | last = Cericola | first = Rachel | date = 2005-09-03 | publisher = TV Fodder | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210126045722/http://www.tvfodder.com/archives/2005/09/fall_tv_5_sitco.shtml | archive-date = 2021-01-26 | accessdate = 2021-02-07 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。2005年4月12日，[[联合派拉蒙电视网|联合派拉蒙电视网]]宣布莎侬·多赫提（{{lang|en|Shannen Doherty}}）已就出演主角开始洽谈，戈麦斯-普雷斯顿在考虑出演主角“长年好友、同事和室友”，艾恩·奥福曼也可能加盟但角色未定<ref name="WingWoman2">{{cite web | url = http://www.thefutoncritic.com/news/2005/04/12/development-update-april-12-18187/6872/ | title = Development Update: April 12 | date = 2005-04-12 | publisher = The Futon Critic | archive-url = https://archive.is/20161121162356/http://www.thefutoncritic.com/news/2005/04/12/development-update-april-12-18187/6872/ | archive-date = 2016-11-21 | dead-url = no | accessdate = 2021-02-07 }}</ref>。奥福曼自称正想接戏，觉得节目构想“很酷”所以有意参与<ref name="starry magazine2">{{cite news | url = http://starrymag.com/ion-overman-where-is-the-love/ | title = Ion Overman – Where Is The Love | work = Starry Constellation Magazine | date = 2014-01-13 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20171219162310/http://starrymag.com/ion-overman-where-is-the-love/ | archive-date = 2017-12-19 | access-date = 2021-02-07 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。4月18日，霍利·罗宾森·皮特确定出演剧中公司老板<ref name="WingWoman3">{{cite web | url = http://www.thefutoncritic.com/news/2005/04/18/development-update-april-18-18219/6877/ | title = Development Update: April 18 | date = 2005-04-18 | publisher = The Futon Critic | archive-url = https://archive.is/20161121162431/http://www.thefutoncritic.com/news/2005/04/18/development-update-april-18-18219/6877/ | archive-date = 2016-11-21 | dead-url = no | accessdate = 2021-02-07 }}</ref>。
