《红娘公司》本是专为捧红多赫提创作，她在试播集扮演丹妮丝<ref name="Doherty5" /><ref name="Doherty3">{{cite book | last = Terrace | first = Vincent | title = Encyclopedia of Television Shows, 1925 through 2010 | year = 2008 | publisher = McFarland | location = Jefferson | isbn = 978-0-7864-6477-7 | page = 628}}</ref>，这也是她首次出演电视[[情景喜剧|情景喜剧]]<ref name="Doherty42">{{cite journal | access-date = 2021-02-07 | url = https://ew.com/article/2006/08/18/shannen-doherty-expert-leaving/ | title = Shannen Doherty is an expert on leaving | last = Labrecque | first = Jeff | date = 2006-08-18 | publisher = [[时代公司|Time Inc.]] | journal = [[娱乐周刊|Entertainment Weekly]] | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210121120714/https://ew.com/article/2006/08/18/shannen-doherty-expert-leaving/ | archive-date = 2021-01-21 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。多赫提自称一眼就喜欢上“歇斯底里的”[[電視試播|试播集]]剧本，但因缺乏喜剧演出经验感到有些不踏实<ref name="DohertyInfinityAndBeyond">{{cite news | url = http://edition.cnn.com/TRANSCRIPTS/0505/19/sbt.01.html | title = TV Stars' Salaries Exposed; Interview With Donald Trump | last = Haffenreffer | first = David | date = 2005-05-19 | publisher = [[有线电视新闻网|CNN]] | work = Showbiz Tonight | access-date = 2021-02-07 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20141102005307/http://edition.cnn.com/TRANSCRIPTS/0505/19/sbt.01.html | archive-date = 2014-11-02 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。早期宣传声称电视剧由多赫提与皮特主演<ref name="Doherty6">{{cite web | url = http://chronicle.augusta.com/stories/2005/05/20/tel_453792.shtml#.V4PrC5MrJE5 | title = Fox, UPN bringing new series to fall schedule | date = 2005-05-20 | publisher = Morris Communications | work = The Augusta Chronicle | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160722082449/http://chronicle.augusta.com/stories/2005/05/20/tel_453792.shtml#.V4PrC5MrJE5 | archive-date = 2016-07-22 | access-date = 2016-07-22 | dead-url = yes }}</ref>，但联合派拉蒙电视网后来宣布必须另找演员取代多赫提才会订购本剧<ref name="Doherty2">{{cite web | access-date = 2021-02-07 | dead-url = no | url = https://www.nndb.com/people/244/000026166/ | title = Shannen Doherty | publisher = Soylent Communications | work = NNDB | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200206110828/https://nndb.com/people/244/000026166/ | archive-date = 2020-02-06 }}</ref>。据《[[电视指南_(美国杂志)|电视指南]]》报导，试映观众对试播集中多赫提的演出反应冷淡<ref name="preview">{{cite journal | url = https://people.com/celebrity/naked-paris-hilton-goes-for-only-46000/ | title = Naked Paris Hilton Goes for Only $46,000 | last2 = Jessen | first2 = Monique | date = 2005-05-26 | publisher = Time Inc | journal = [[人物_(雜誌)|People]] | last1 = Silverman | first1 = Stephen M. | access-date = 2021-02-07 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160914200341/http://www.people.com/people/article/0,,1065841,00.html | archive-date = 2016-09-14 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。执行制作人沃伦·利特菲尔德（{{lang|en|Warren Littlefield}}）在接受采访时表示，多赫提扮演的丹妮丝“艳光四射”，估计是在离开《[[飛越比佛利|飛越比佛利]]》和《[[聖女魔咒|聖女魔咒]]》剧组后想出演本剧改善负面形象。皮特称赞多赫提的演出，还称“我们都很开心，气氛很棒”。联合派拉蒙电视网娱乐总裁表示，另找演员取代多赫提不过是因为电视台决定让节目朝不同方向发展。<ref name="Doherty1">{{cite news | access-date = 2021-02-07 | url = https://news.google.com/newspapers?nid=1696&dat=20050724&id=XSUqAAAAIBAJ&pg=4351,3028374&hl=en | title = 'Love, Inc.' crew sticks up for booted Doherty | last = Porter | first = Rick | date = 2005-07-24 | publisher = Zap2it | archive-url = https://archive.is/20161109202656/https://news.google.com/newspapers?nid=1696&dat=20050724&id=XSUqAAAAIBAJ&sjid=QkgEAAAAIBAJ&pg=4351,3028374&hl=en | archive-date = 2016-11-09 | dead-url = no }}</ref>电视饲料网站刊登雷切尔·塞里科拉（{{lang|en|Rachel Cericola}}）的文章，称《红娘公司》因更换多赫提引起媒体关注，跻身“新电视季最有前途的四部情景喜剧”<ref name="Fodder2" />。

7月25日，联合派拉蒙电视网宣布贝茜·菲利普斯获选出演丹妮丝，随后将她定为节目领衔主演<ref name="Doherty42"/><ref name="BusyAsDenise">{{cite web | access-date = 2021-02-07 | url = http://www.thefutoncritic.com/news/2005/07/25/busy-philipps-joins-the-cast-of-upns-new-comedy-love-inc--18853/20050725upn01/ | title = Busy Philipps Joins the Cast of UPN's New Comedy "Love, InC." | publisher = The Futon Critic | archive-url = https://archive.is/20161121162530/http://www.thefutoncritic.com/news/2005/07/25/busy-philipps-joins-the-cast-of-upns-new-comedy-love-inc--18853/20050725upn01/ | archive-date = 2016-11-21 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。菲利普斯2018年的回忆录自称对当年联合派拉蒙电视网替换多赫提颇感不平，所以一度不想接演：“他们先利用她大肆宣传，事了后又一脚踢开，如此行径实在太不地道”<ref name="2019Additions4">{{cite book | last = Philipps | first = Busy | title = This Will Only Hurt a Little | year = 2018 | publisher = Simon and Schuster | location = New York | isbn = 978-1-5011-8471-0 | pages = 220, 226}}</ref>。文斯·维鲁夫认为，以菲利普斯取代多赫提后，节目就由以丹妮丝为核心变成[[群戲|群戲]]演出，红娘公司所有成员都是主角。在他看来，观众“可能会对节目只关注某人爱情生活的酸甜苦辣感到厌烦”，这样的改动能避免上述俗套。<ref name="starry magazine" />

有报导称[[佩吉·肯尼迪|佩吉·肯尼迪]]（{{lang|en|Page Kennedy}}）一度考虑参演本剧，但后来决定在[[美国广播公司|美国广播公司]]电视剧《[[绝望的主妇|绝望的主妇]]》[[靚太唔易做_(第二季)|第二季]]扮演卡莱布·阿普尔怀特（{{lang|en|Caleb Applewhite}}）<ref name="Applewhite">{{cite news | url = https://www.cbsnews.com/news/desperate-housewives-actor-fired/ | title = 'Desperate Housewives' Actor Fired | last = Pace | first = Gina | date = 2005-11-08 | publisher = CBS Broadcasting inc. | work = [[CBS新聞|CBS News]] | archive-date = 2020-11-24 | access-date = 2021-02-07 | dead-url = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201124050035/https://www.cbsnews.com/news/desperate-housewives-actor-fired/ }}</ref>。[[洛杉矶湖人|洛杉矶湖人]]退役球员[[里克·福克斯|里克·福克斯]]在三集节目[[客串|客串]]出镜，诠释克丽娅的男友大卫<ref name="RickFox">{{cite news | url = https://www.latimes.com/archives/la-xpm-2005-nov-03-sp-briefing3-story.html | title = Kissing Is Part of Job When Fox Is in 'Love | last = Stewart | first = Larry | date = 2005-11-03 | publisher = Tronc, Inc. | newspaper = [[洛杉磯時報|Los Angeles Times]] | archive-date = 2015-12-03 | access-date = 2021-02-07 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20151203055057/http://articles.latimes.com/2005/nov/03/sports/sp-briefing3 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。[[萨塞克斯公爵夫人梅根|梅根·马克尔]]在分集《一对一》（{{lang|en|One on One}}）客串出演地铁工作人员<ref name="MeghanSource1">{{cite web | archive-date = 2020-09-27 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200927200710/https://www.cosmopolitan.com/entertainment/celebs/a19724525/meghan-markle-movies-tv-show-list/ | title = A Definitive List of Every TV Show and Movie Meghan Markle Has Been In | url = https://www.cosmopolitan.com/entertainment/celebs/a19724525/meghan-markle-movies-tv-show-list/ | last = Truong | first = Peggy | date = 2018-04-10 | work = [[柯夢波丹|Cosmopolitan]] | access-date = 2021-02-07 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。联合派拉蒙电视网秉持“唯一积极为非裔美国观众提供节目的电视网”立场，本剧演员阵容同样趋于种族多元化。蒂姆·古德（{{lang|en|Tim Good}}）在《[[旧金山纪事报|旧金山纪事报]]》发文指出，本剧制作仅有选角值得认可。<ref name="WhiteWash">{{cite news | url = https://www.sfgate.com/entertainment/article/As-if-TV-weren-t-white-enough-when-the-WB-2497933.php | title = As if TV weren't white enough ... when the WB, UPN go off the air, guess who loses out? | last = Good | first = Tim | date = 2006-05-03 | publisher = [[赫斯特国际集团|Hearst Corporation]] | newspaper = [[旧金山纪事报|San Francisco Chronicle]] | access-date = 2021-02-07 | dead-url = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180927085516/https://www.sfgate.com/entertainment/article/As-if-TV-weren-t-white-enough-when-the-WB-2497933.php | archive-date = 2018-09-27 }}</ref>

剧中情节发生在纽约，实际是在好莱坞[[派拉蒙影業|派拉蒙制片厂]]布鲁多恩大厦（{{lang|en|Bluhdorn Building}}）取景<ref name="InitialOrder">{{cite web | access-date = 2021-02-07 | archive-date = 2018-09-27 | dead-url = no | url = https://www.backstage.com/magazine/article/nbc-upn-wb-fall-primetime-network-programs-18502/ | title = NBC, UPN & The WB Fall 2005 Primetime Network Programs | date = 2005-08-06 | publisher = Backstage, LLC | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180927204451/https://www.backstage.com/magazine/article/nbc-upn-wb-fall-primetime-network-programs-18502/ | work = Backstage }}</ref>，采用[[多镜头模式|多镜头模式]]<ref name="Cameras" />。自由撰稿人[[艾伦·科尔仕|艾伦·科尔仕]]创作第19集剧本<ref name="2019Additions1" />。除试播集外，其他分集标题都是过去的情景喜剧名称<ref name="Premise2" />。过渡画面采用纽约市景观，并配上当代音乐，如[[黑眼豆豆|黑眼豆豆]]2005年单曲《[[勿伤我心|勿伤我心]]》（{{lang|en|Don't Phunk with My Heart}}）、[[凯丽思|凯丽思]]（{{lang|en|Kelis}}）2003年单曲《[[奶昔_(歌曲)|奶昔]]》（{{lang|en|Milkshake}}）。《[[PopMatters|PopMatters]]》的托德·拉姆洛（{{lang|en|Todd R. Ramlow}}）认为，这些音乐旨在进一步吸引包括黑人与白人在内的城镇居民收看，他称赞“通常面向黑人目标观众的电视台愿意尝试”吸引其他族裔<ref name="Premise1" />。

