 time to get real | last2 = Cooper | first2 = Gael Fashingbauer | date = 2006-01-25 | publisher = [[NBC新聞|NBC News]] | last1 = Bonné | first1 = Jon | work = [[今天_(NBC)|Today]] | dead-url = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160722081540/http://www.today.com/id/11007437/ns/today-today_entertainment/t/two-networks-pair-its-time-get-real/ | archive-date = 2016-07-22 | access-date = 2021-02-08 }}</ref>，联合派拉蒙电视网除本剧外还同期推出《[[阿傑出少年|阿傑出少年]]》、《[[伊芙_(电视剧)|伊芙]]》（''{{lang|en|Eve}}''）与《[[理发店_(电视剧)|理发店]]》（''{{lang|en|Cuts}}''）<ref name="Doherty6" />。电视网还把《[[SmackDown_LIVE|WWE SmackDown]]》改到周五播出，周四集中播放情景喜剧，希望把周四打造成“剧本节目之夜”，吸引电影制片商为宣传新片投放广告<ref name="Sun1">{{cite news | url = https://www.sun-sentinel.com/news/fl-xpm-2005-05-20-0505200092-story.html | title = Upn Wrestles With Schedule | last = Jicha | first = Tom | date = 2005-05-20 | publisher = Tribune Publishing | newspaper = Sun-Sentinel | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190327122946/https://www.sun-sentinel.com/news/fl-xpm-2005-05-20-0505200092-story.html | archive-date = 2019-03-27 | dead-url = no | access-date = 2021-02-08 | 12 =  }}</ref>《[[今天_(NBC)|今天]]》栏目认为《红娘公司》与《阿傑出少年》未必会像电视台期待的那样吸引相同观众群<ref name="SoBad" />，两剧品质也不在同一水平面，《红娘公司》要差得多<ref name="Unbearable" />。《阿傑出少年》的观众起初有59%继续收看《红娘公司》<ref name="TotalRatings">{{cite web | url = http://www.thefutoncritic.com/news/2005/11/05/upn-to-keep-the-love-going-for-the-full-season-19721/7028/ | title = UPN to Keep the 'Love' Going for the Full Season | last = Sullivan | first = Brian Ford | publisher = The Futon Critic | archive-url = https://archive.today/20161121165432/http://www.thefutoncritic.com/news/2005/11/05/upn-to-keep-the-love-going-for-the-full-season-19721/7028/ | archive-date = 2016-11-21 | dead-url = no | access-date = 2021-02-08 }}</ref>，但后来逐渐流失大部分受众，证明电视台的宣传策略失当<ref name="Fail">{{cite news | url = https://www.nytimes.com/2005/09/24/arts/arts-briefly-viewers-love-chris.html | title = Arts, Briefly; Viewers Love 'Chris' | last = Aurthur | first = Kate | date = 2005-09-24 | publisher = The New York Times Company | newspaper = The New York Times | access-date = 2021-02-08 | dead-url = no | page = B10 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190327124603/https://www.nytimes.com/2005/09/24/arts/arts-briefly-viewers-love-chris.html | archive-date = 2019-03-27 }}</ref>。

据塞里科拉报导，《红娘公司》每集约有360万观众收看<ref name="FullOrder" />，《[[荷里活報道|荷里活報道]]》发文声称节目在18至49岁年龄段的[[尼爾森收視率|尼爾森收視率]]成绩是1.0/3，在2005至2006年电视季[[地面電視|地面]][[電視聯播網|電視聯播網]]节目中排第141<ref name="Ratings1">{{Cite journal | archive-date = 2010-07-22 | access-date = 2010-07-22 | url = https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/hr/search/article_display.jsp?vnu_content_id=1002576393 | title = Series | date = 2006-05-26 | publisher = [[普羅米修斯環球媒體|Prometheus Global Media]] | journal = [[荷里活報道|The Hollywood Reporter]] | dead-url = yes | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20100722095055/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/hr/search/article_display.jsp?vnu_content_id=1002576393 }}</ref>。[[尼爾森NV|尼尔森公司]]的统计表明，节目在“12至17岁拉美裔”人群的收视率很高，在2005年收视人数中占绝大部分，达340万人。《红娘公司》在12至17岁拉美裔女观众群的收视成绩好过联合派拉蒙电视网情景喜剧《[[一对一_(电视剧)|一对一]]》和《[[一半一半_(电视剧)|一半一半]]》（''{{lang|en|Half & Half}}''）。<ref name="Latina2">{{cite book | last = Servaes | first = Jan | title = Sustainability, Participation & Culture in Communication: Theory and Praxis | year = 2013 | publisher = Intellect Books | location = Bristol | isbn = 978-1-84150-661-6 | page = 347}}</ref>，观众总人数在联合派拉蒙电视网所有电视剧中位居上游<ref name="TotalRatings" />。与上一年电视季的同一时间段相比，节目首播在18至49岁年龄段观众群的收视率上涨六个百分点，18至34岁女观众增幅五成三，18至49岁女观众增加118%<ref name="WomenRatings">{{cite web | archive-url = https://archive.today/20161121165506/http://www.thefutoncritic.com/news/2005/09/27/upns-strategy-of-targeting-young-women-pays-off-top-model-and-chris-premieres-lead-upn-to-its-best-week-ever-as-a-five-night-network-among-women-18-34-19359/20050927upn02/ | archive-date = 2016-11-21 | dead-url = no | access-date = 2021-02-08 | url = http://www.thefutoncritic.com/news/2005/09/27/upns-strategy-of-targeting-young-women-pays-off-top-model-and-chris-premieres-lead-upn-to-its-best-week-ever-as-a-five-night-network-among-women-18-34-19359/20050927upn02/ | title = UPN's Strategy of Targeting Young Women Pays Off! "Top Model" and "Chris" Premieres Lead UPN to Its Best Week Ever as a Five Night Network Among Women 18–34 | publisher = The Futon Critic }}</ref>。

联合派拉蒙电视网2006年与[[WB電視網|WB電視網]]合并组建[[CW電視網|CW電視網]]，《红娘公司》及联合派拉蒙电视网大部分节目停播<ref name="Latina">{{cite book | last = McCann | first = Bob | title = Encyclopedia of African American Actresses in Film and Television | year = 2009 | publisher = McFarland | location = Jefferson | isbn = 978-0-7864-3790-0 | page = 291}}</ref>。《[[危机_(杂志)|危机]]》（''{{lang|en|The Crisis}}''）杂志的弗恩·吉莱斯皮（{{lang|en|Fern Gillespie}}）谴责CW電視網甫一成立就“一口气消灭八部非裔美国人喜剧中的五部”，还对[[美國三大電視網|美國三大電視網]]都没几部非裔美国人情景喜剧深感失望：“青年艺术家没有磨练技能的机遇，可能会影响整整一代人”<ref name="Crisis">{{cite book | publisher = [[美国全国有色人种协进会|NAACP]] | work = The Crisis | url = https://books.google.com.tw/books?id=w0IEAAAAMBAJ&q="love%2C+inc."+"upn"&pg=PA57#v=snippet&q=%22love%2C%20inc.%22%20%22upn%22&f=false | title = Major Networks Black Out African American Comedies | last = Gillespie | first = Fern | date = 2006-10 | access-date = 2021-02-08 | archive-date = 2016-07-22 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160722081316/https://books.google.com/books?id=w0IEAAAAMBAJ&pg=PA57&lpg=PA57&dq=%22love%2C%20inc.%22%20%22upn%22&source=bl&ots=PctW3ECooz&sig=McWHaGOVfG6D7ZNW4ZClaZHXfsY&hl=en&sa=X&ved=0ahUKEwjZv7333OrNAhVSID4KHesQCTk4MhDoAQgoMAI#v=snippet&q=%22love%2C%20inc.%22%20%22upn%22&f=false | dead-url = no }}</ref>。评论家蒂姆·古德曼（{{lang|en|Tim Goodman}}）指出，两家公司合并造成六部面向非裔美国人的节目取消，其中《红娘公司》还是非裔女演员主演。在他看来，这些节目取消代表各大电视网“逐渐淘汰利基市场节目”。<ref name="Niche">{{cite book | last = Warner | first = Kristen J. | title = The Cultural Politics of Colorblind TV | year = 2015 | publisher = Routledge | location = New York | isbn = 978-1-138-01830-3 | page = 98}}</ref>《红娘公司》没有通过蓝光影碟或DVD发行<ref name="Premise2" /><ref name="NoDVDForYou">{{cite web | url = http://www.tvshowsondvd.com/shows/Love/9477 | title = Love, Inc. (2005) | publisher = TV Guide Online | work = TVShowsOnDVD.com | archive-date = 2016-09-16 | access-date = 2016-09-16 | dead-url = yes | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160916121602/http://www.tvshowsondvd.com/shows/Love/9477 }}</ref>。

=== 专业评价 ===
[[File:Holly_Robinson_Peete_in_July_2010.jpg|thumb]]提名]]

《红娘公司》播出后反响不一。《[[乌木_(杂志)|乌木]]》（''{{lang|en|Ebony}}''）杂志的宗德拉·休斯（{{lang|en|Zondra Hughes}}）认为本剧在非裔美国演员主演的黄金时段电视节目中颇具潜力，其中又以皮特和奥福曼最为耀眼<ref name="StarAppeal">{{Cite book | archive-date = 2019-02-15 | dead-url = no | access-date = 2021-02-08 | url = https://books.google.com/books?id=8csDAAAAMBAJ&pg=RA1-PA194-IA2&lpg=RA1-PA194-IA2&dq=%22love%2C%20inc.%22%20%22upn%22&source=bl&ots=NZ-UZqGjsU&sig=GOJckUayAYGESkj_z59vZrueS88&hl=en&sa=X&ved=0ahUKEwjd__XK0-rNAhWEFz4KHQA-DDk4ChDoAQhBMAc | title = Prime-Time 2005: More Stars, More Soul, More Sensation | last = Hughes | first = Zondrat | date = 2005-10 | publisher = Ebony Media Corporation | work = Ebony | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190215055156/https://books.google.com/books?id=8csDAAAAMBAJ&pg=RA1-PA194-IA2&lpg=RA1-PA194-IA2&dq=%22love%2C%20inc.%22%20%22upn%22&source=bl&ots=NZ-UZqGjsU&sig=GOJckUayAYGESkj_z59vZrueS88&hl=en&sa=X&ved=0ahUKEwjd__XK0-rNAhWEFz4KHQA-DDk4ChDoAQhBMAc }}</ref>。节目在{{lang|en|LivingTV}}开播后，《[[每日紀事報|每日紀事報]]》发文将其列入“每日精选”，建议喜欢喜剧的观众收看<ref name="Giggle" />。黛安·沃特斯（{{lang|en|Diane Werts}}）在《[[新闻日报_(纽约)|新闻日报]]》（''{{lang|en|Newsday}}''）发文，称赞剧中人物形象鲜明、分工明确，编剧“点到即止，尽显明智”<ref name="ACMC">{{cite web | url = https://www.metacritic.com/tv/love-inc?ftag=MCD-06-10aaa1c | title = Love, Inc. : Season 1 | publisher = [[Metacritic|Metacritic]] | access-date = 2021-02-08 | dead-url = no | archive-date = 2018-08-10 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180810070730/http://www.metacritic.com/tv/love-inc?ftag=MCD-06-10aaa1c }}</ref>。皮特在[[第37届有色人种进步协会形象奖|第37届]][[有色人种进步协会形象奖|有色人种进步协会形象奖]]角逐中获[[有色人种进步协会形象奖喜剧类最佳女演员|喜剧类最佳女演员奖]]提名<ref name="NAACPAwardPeete">{{cite web | url = http://www.thefutoncritic.com/news/2006/01/10/randy-jackson-aisha-tyler-kimberly-elise-james-pickens-jr-and-kevin-frazier-join-new-naacp-president-and-ceo-bruce-s-gordon-to-announce-the-37th-naacp-image-awards-nominations--20236/20060110fox01/ | title = Randy Jackson, Aisha Tyler, Kimberly Elise, James Pickens JR., and Kevin Frazier Join New Naacp President and Ceo Bruce S. Gordon to Announce the "37th Naacp Image Awards" Nominations | date = 2006-01-10 | publisher = The Futon Critic | archive-url = https://archive.today/20130707031931/http://www.thefutoncritic.com/news/2006/01/10/randy-jackson-aisha-tyler-kimberly-elise-james-pickens-jr-and-kevin-frazier-join-new-naacp-president-and-ceo-bruce-s-gordon-to-announce-the-37th-naacp-image-awards-nominations--20236/20060110fox01/ | archive-date = 2013-07-07 | dead-url = no | accessdate = 2021-02-08 }}</ref>，但不敌出演《阿傑出少年》的[[蒂琪娜·阿诺|蒂琪娜·阿诺]]（{{lang|en|Tichina Arnold}}）<ref name="NAACPAwardPeete2">{{cite news | archive-date = 2016-08-07 | access-date = 2016-08-07 | url = http://www.hurriyetdailynews.com/winners-of-the-37th-annual-naacp-image-awards.aspx?pageID=438&n=winners-of-the-37th-annual-naacp-image-awards-2006-02-27 | title = Winners of the 37th annual NAACP Image Awards | date = 2006-02-27 | publisher = Doğan Media Group | work = Hürriyet Daily News | dead-url = yes | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160807160912/http://www.hurriyetdailynews.com/winners-of-the-37th-annual-naacp-image-awards.aspx?pageID=438&n=winners-of-the-37th-annual-naacp-image-awards-2006-02-27 }}</ref>。据菲利普斯所述，[[昆汀·塔伦蒂诺|昆汀·塔伦蒂诺]]是本剧粉丝<ref name="2019Additions4" />。

[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]根据17份评论为本剧打分28（最高100），表明节目整体反响不佳<ref name="ACMC" />。[[The_Futon_Critic|The Futon Critic]]的布莱恩·福特·沙利文（{{lang|en|Brian Ford Sullivan}}）称赞文斯·维鲁夫戏份不多但表现特别亮眼，不过对婚介工作的刻画不及2005年电影《全民情敌》<ref name="Hitch" />。劳拉·弗里斯（{{lang|en|Laura Fries}}）在《[[綜藝_(雜誌)|综艺]]》杂志发文，称本剧氛围怪异，演员颇具风度，剧本干净利落，但剧情和人物缺乏新意<ref name="OldMaid" />。《今天》的乔恩·波内（{{lang|en|Jon Bonné}}）和盖尔·法辛鲍尔·库珀（{{lang|en|Gael Fashingbauer Cooper}}）认可剧中请来各族裔演员演出，但感觉喜剧内容贫乏，演员再怎么竭力表现也难以回天<ref name="SoBad" />。《[[洛杉磯時報|洛杉磯時報]]》刊登保罗·布朗菲尔德（{{lang|en|Paul Brownfield}}）的文章，批评《红娘公司》喜剧效果实在欠佳，明显不及[[HBO|HBO]]情景喜剧《[[喜開二度|喜開二度]]》<ref name="Advisory" />。莫琳·瑞安（{{lang|en|Maureen Ryan}}）在《芝加哥论坛报》发文指出，本剧在《阿傑出少年》之后播出，注定会被辗压成碎片，估计很快就会如同注脚般消失在历史长河<ref name="Chicago" />。

评论员对菲利普斯的演出与丹妮斯的人物塑造反响不佳，觉得角色令人感到厌烦，无法让观众感同身受。弗吉尼亚·赫弗南（{{lang|en|Virginia Heffernan}}）就觉得丹妮丝不像1995年电影《[[獨領風騷|獨領風騷]]》中[[艾莉西亞·席薇史東|艾丽西亚·希尔维斯通]]扮演的雪儿·霍洛维兹（{{lang|en|Cher Horowitz}}）那样充满魅力<ref name="Doherty5" />。《[[今日美國|今日美國]]》的罗伯特·比安科（{{lang|en|Robert Bianco}}）对节目评分仅半星（最高四星），称菲利普斯的表演就是在“动个不停：面部扭曲、身体抽搐，仿佛总是像驴子般尖叫”，令节目变得“实在难以忍受”<ref name="Unbearable" />。马修·吉尔伯特（{{lang|en|Matthew Gilbert}}）在《[[波士頓環球報|波士頓環球報]]》发文，认为节目内容空洞，把单个笑料无限拉长，丹妮丝背景类似《[[俏红娘|俏红娘]]》中艾丽西亚·希尔维斯通的角色，但就是让人提不起兴趣<ref name="MissMatch" />。《[[匹兹堡邮报|匹兹堡邮报]]》刊登罗布·欧文（{{lang|en|Rob Owen}}）的评论，认为多赫提更适合扮演丹妮丝，“自信满满”的形象加分不少，菲利普斯的演出让他感到“眼花缭乱、神经质，纯粹就是疯子”<ref name="NutCase">{{cite news | access-date = 2021-02-08 | url = https://www.post-gazette.com/ae/tv/2005/09/22/On-the-Tube-HBO-serves-up-Sunday-Night-comedy-with-Extras-Curb/stories/200509220377 | title = On the Tube: HBO serves up Sunday Night comedy with 'Extras,' "Curb' | last = Owen | first = Rob | date = 2005-09-22 | newspaper = [[匹兹堡邮报|Pittsburgh Post-Gazette]] | publisher = Block Communications | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20170724011250/http://www.post-gazette.com/ae/tv/2005/09/22/On-the-Tube-HBO-serves-up-Sunday-Night-comedy-with-Extras-Curb/stories/200509220377 | archive-date = 2017-07-24 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。拉姆洛认为，与《[[慾望城市|慾望城市]]》相比，本剧的女角色费尽心机依旧-{表}-现拙劣，能力实在有限<ref name="Premise1" />。

